        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Wastewater Infrastructure Modernization Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Environmental Protection Agency to establish a program to award grants to municipalities for projects at publicly owned treatment works concerning (1) intelligent sewage or stormwater collection systems, or (2) innovative and alternative combined storm and sanitary sewer projects.</p>]]>
        </text>
